<refnamediv>
  <refname>pbesrewr</refname>
  <refpurpose>rewrites and simplify a PBES</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
  <cmdsynopsis>
    <command>&pbesrewr;</command>
    <arg choice="plain" rep="repeat"><arg choice="opt">&option;</arg></arg>
    <arg choice="opt">&infile;</arg>
    <arg choice="opt">&outfile;</arg>
  </cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1>
  <title>Description</title>
  <para>
    Rewrite the data expressions in a PBES, simplify and and or expressions and
    remove quantified variables that are not used
    in &infile;.  If &infile; is not supplied a PBES is read from &stdin;. 
    The output is written to &outfile;, or if not supplied to &stdout;.
  </para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1>
  <title>Options</title>
  <para>
    <variablelist>

      <varlistentry>
        <term>&opt_h;</term>
        <term>&opt_help;</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>display help information and exit</para>
          </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term>&opt_version;</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>display version information and exit</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      
      <varlistentry>
        <term>&opt_v;</term>
        <term>&opt_verbose;</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>displays progress information during the run of the program.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      
      <varlistentry>
        <term>&opt_d;</term>
        <term>&opt_debug;</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>displays debug information during the run of the program.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term>&opt_R;</term>
        <term>&opt_rewriter;</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>Allows to select a rewriter. Possibilities are inner, jitty, innerc and jittyc.
                Inner stands for the innermost rewriter, jitty for the just in time rewriter.
                If a c is added, then the compiling rewriter is used. Compiling rewriting is 
                not available on windows. 
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

    </variablelist>
  </para>
</refsect1>

